title: Unchained Alistar
body:
Attempting to use the link to redeem the unchained Alistar only brings up a blank page.
I have subscribed to the YouTube channel.
But am unable to discover how to get skin through normal means.
. And the second page where the http://youtube.na.leagueoflegends.com/en/youtube brings up a blank page.
If unchained Alistar is no longer available I understand, and this ticket can be disregarded after I am notified of such. Otherwise can someone please direct me on how to resolve this issue?
Thank you,
StueckSalat

replies.body:
Sometimes the link breaks! D:

We can help you out if you submit a [support request](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/requests/new), where one of our specialists will get back to you.

Let me know if you have any questions.
